ObjectListItem Class

Definition

Represents an individual item within an ObjectListItemCollection. For information about how to develop ASP.NET mobile applications, see the www.asp.net/mobile Web site.

Remarks

An ObjectListItem object is created implicitly only during data binding. Do not declare it directly on a page.
